OL,3,CChallenge over former school welfare
OL,4,Cofficer's sex abuse prison term fails
OL,6,FProsecutors failed in a legal
OL,7,Fchallenge to the prison term imposed
OL,8,Fon a former school welfare officer and
OL,9,FArmy Cadet leader for sexually abusing
OL,10,Fteenage girls.
OL,12,FJudges in the Court of Appeal rejected
OL,13,Fclaims the sentencing of Co Down man
OL,14,FNeil Beckett was unduly lenient.
OL,16,FBeckett, 44, from Kilmore Village near
OL,17,FCrossgar, was found guilty of sexual
OL,18,Fassault and inappropriate contact with
OL,19,Fnine teenage victims he targeted while
OL,20,Fholding a position of authority.
