OL,3,CChallenge over former school welfare
OL,4,Cofficer's sex abuse prison term fails
OL,6,FThe charges against him related to
OL,7,Fseven pupils at Lagan College School
OL,8,Fin south Belfast and two Army Cadets,
OL,9,Fspanning a period between 2015 and
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FIn December last year he received a
OL,13,Fthree-year sentence at Belfast Crown
OL,14,FCourt, with 18 months to be served in
OL,15,Fprison and 18 months on licence.
OL,17,FBeckett was also put on the sex
OL,18,Foffenders' register indefinitely and
OL,19,Fmade subject to a Sexual Offence
OL,20,FProtection Order (SOPO) for five years.
