OL,3,CChallenge over former school welfare
OL,4,Cofficer's sex abuse prison term fails
OL,6,FThe sentencing judge identified the
OL,7,Fabuse of trust and authority, along
OL,8,Fwith the victims' vulnerabilities, as
OL,9,Faggravating factors.
OL,11,FHe also cited elements of grooming
OL,12,Fwhich continued after the defendant
OL,13,Fwas made aware of the complaints
OL,14,Fagainst him.
OL,16,FBeckett denied all of the allegations
OL,17,Fwhile on trial for a total of 29
OL,18,Fcharges.
