OL,3,CChallenge over former school welfare
OL,4,Cofficer's sex abuse prison term fails
OL,6,FThe abuse involved hugging, kissing
OL,7,Fand tickling pupils, as well as
OL,8,Ftouching some of the girls under their
OL,9,Fskirts.
OL,11,FHe was ultimately acquitted on a
OL,12,Fcharge of rape, but found guilty of a
OL,13,Fcarrying out a series of sexual
OL,14,Fassaults.
OL,16,FBeckett initially mounted a legal
OL,17,Fchallenge against conviction before
OL,18,Feventually abandoning the bid to clear
OL,19,Fhis name.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
