OL,3,CChallenge over former school welfare
OL,4,Cofficer's sex abuse prison term fails
OL,6,FBut in a separate move, the Public
OL,7,FProsecution Service (PPS) referred the
OL,8,Fcase to the Court of Appeal in an
OL,9,Fattempt to have the sentence declared
OL,10,Funduly lenient.
OL,12,FCounsel for the PPS argued that the
OL,13,Fassessment of Beckett's culpability
OL,14,Fand the harm he caused to his
OL,15,Fvulnerable victims was not properly
OL,16,Fdealt with.
OL,18,FIt was also claimed that the prison
OL,19,Fterm was outside the appropriate range.
