OL,4,Cofficer's sex abuse prison term fails
OL,6,FDefence lawyers accepted there were
OL,7,Faggravating features, including the
OL,8,Fimpact his offences had on the teenage
OL,9,Fgirls.
OL,11,FBut they insisted that a proportionate
OL,12,Fsentence was imposed following an
OL,13,Fassessment of all the circumstances.
OL,15,FThe court also heard Beckett has lost
OL,16,Fcareer opportunities and is set to
OL,17,Fremain on the sex offenders register
OL,18,Findefinitely.
