OL,3,CChallenge over former school welfare
OL,4,Cofficer's sex abuse prison term fails
OL,6,FDelivering judgment, Lady Chief
OL,7,FJustice Dame Siobhan Keegan rejected
OL,8,Fall grounds of challenge.
OL,10,F"This was always a case of high
OL,11,Fculpability, that was accepted by the
OL,12,Fdefence, and therefore the
OL,13,Fprosecution's argument that we should
OL,14,Fincrease the sentence based on the
OL,15,F(trial) judge's mischaracterisation of
OL,16,Fculpability is unsustainable," she
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FShe added: "The judge has faithfully
OL,20,Fapplied the (sentencing) guidance."
