OL,6,FDespite dismissing the PPS reference,
OL,7,FDame Siobhan stressed that the
OL,8,Fvictim's had been "entirely
OL,9,Fvindicated" by Beckett's decision to
OL,10,Fabandon his appeal against conviction.
OL,12,F"No sentence can fully fix the impact
OL,13,Fof this offending on the lives of
OL,14,Fyoung girls," she added.
OL,16,FBut speaking outside court, the father
OL,17,Fof one of Beckett's victims expressed
OL,18,Fdisappointment at the outcome.
